Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Strike Hawk has taken Kamui back. His maintenance will be handled by them this time.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "That's how it should be in the first place.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'His wounds must be really bad that he needs to be treated at their own place.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: '(Nods) Kamui has helped us so much. I hope he can get through this.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Even with all the bad memory he has remembered...', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Perhaps it's a good thing that he doesn't do a lot of thinking then.", 4: '1'}
{2: "That's his strength.", 3: '19', 4: "That is what's unique about him.", 5: '19'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Commandant, you really like Kamui, don't you?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "After what we've been through, I feel like Kamui is already one of us.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "It's just... it might be strange for us to say it, but emotionally speaking, I think he's indeed part of the team.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: '"Emotion" does sound strange coming from a Construct.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Not that I can say anything to disagree.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "It's rare to see Lee and Liv agreeing on something like this.", 4: '1'}
